    "body" : "<p><a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/212321/anyone-know-a-simple-way-using-java-calendar-to-subtract-x-days-to-a-date#212334\">Anson's answer</a> will work fine for the simple case, but if you're going to do any more complex date calculations I'd recommend checking out <a href=\"http://joda-time.sourceforge.net/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Joda Time</a>.  It will make your life much easier.</p>\n\n<p>FYI in Joda Time you could do</p>\n\n<pre><code>DateTime dt = new DateTime();\nDateTime fiveDaysEarlier = dt.minusDays(5);\n</code></pre>\n"
