    "body" : "<p>Eli Courtwright second solution is wrong, it should be:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Calendar c = Calendar.getInstance();\nc.setTime(date);\nc.add(Calendar.DATE, -days);\ndate.setTime(c.getTime().getTime());\n</code></pre>\n"
